  "text": "We give a construction of an infinite family of quantum secret sharing schemes (3) log(5) < n − n 0.68 . This construction can be defined recursively from cycle over 5 vertices (C 5 ) which has been used in Markham and Sanders [CITATION_1] to build a ((3,5)) quantum secret sharing protocol.",
